               <code code="34088-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="OVERDOSAGE SECTION"/>
               <title>OVERDOSAGE</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Topically applied Clindamycin Phosphate Topical Solution USP, 1% can be absorbed in sufficient amounts to produce systemic effects (see
 
  <content styleCode="bold">
                        <linkHtml href="#ID_71a8caba-4d8e-4323-876d-5b665b15fb17">WARNINGS</linkHtml>
                     </content>).

 </paragraph>
               </text>
