               <code code="34068-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DOSAGE &amp; ADMINISTRATION SECTION"/>
               <title>DOSAGE AND ADMINISTRATION</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Apply a thin film of Clindamycin Phosphate Topical Solution USP, 1% twice daily to affected area. Keep container tightly closed.</paragraph>
